name: Cosmic Tarot
profile:
I promote, encourage and endorse personal healing and self love through compassionate inner dialogue and introspective insight of ones own mental and emotional state. Through self love and acceptance we will find the ability and power to transform our lives into the reality that best benefits our highest good. 

Tarot Reading is an ancient practice of divination that deals with understanding the relationships between energies amongst us all. Tarot is a great tool to use for understanding oneself more and in a deeper manner. The hidden becomes revealed and the lost become found when we start to take a look inwards to our situations and energetic expressions in a situation.
